g.text: An administrator resolves violation of statute reports.
A software author resolves bug reports (regarding his/her software unit).
A software unit contains an executable.
A software unit is made of source code.
A software author manages his/her software unit.
A violation report regards a software unit.
A user reports violations of statute.
A bug report regards a software unit.
Visual Paradigm Standard(Igor Sosnowicz(Wrocław University of Science and Technology))
